    {
      "start": 685.65,
      "end": 687.13,
      "text": "he's doing some PR"
    },
    {
      "start": 687.13,
      "end": 688.45,
      "text": "because he likes her"
    },
    {
      "start": 688.45,
      "end": 690.91,
      "text": "that means he's brave enough"
    },
    {
      "start": 690.91,
      "end": 692.15,
      "text": "I don't think so"
    },
    {
      "start": 692.15,
      "end": 693.33,
      "text": "he says he's brave enough"
    },
    {
      "start": 693.33,
      "end": 695.11,
      "text": "but often times guys like this"
    },
    {
      "start": 695.11,
      "end": 696.81,
      "text": "they're all talk no show"
    },
    {
      "start": 696.81,
      "end": 698.67,
      "text": "let's 지켜봐야죠"
    },
    {
      "start": 698.67,
      "end": 699.41,
      "text": "그렇죠 그렇죠"
    },
    {
      "start": 699.41,
      "end": 700.53,
      "text": "허세일 수도 있습니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 700.53,
      "end": 703.13,
      "text": "긴장의 끈을 놓으면 안 될 것 같아요"
    },
    {
      "start": 703.13,
      "end": 707.59,
      "text": "네 한 번 더 들어보시죠"
    },
    {
      "start": 707.59,
      "end": 708.89,
      "text": "didn't you just move into"
    },
    {
      "start": 708.89,
      "end": 710.97,
      "text": "the creepiest house in town?"
    },
    {
      "start": 711.71,
      "end": 714.37,
      "text": "you should know that nobody stays for long in that house"
    },
    {
      "start": 714.37,
      "end": 716.43,
      "text": "we never stay anywhere for long"
    },
    {
      "start": 716.43,
      "end": 717.95,
      "text": "but you should be careful"
    },
    {
      "start": 717.95,
      "end": 721.25,
      "text": "there have been some spine-chilling tales of that place"
    },
    {
      "start": 721.25,
      "end": 722.51,
      "text": "come on"
    },
    {
      "start": 722.51,
      "end": 724.67,
      "text": "everything has a logical explanation"
    },
    {
      "start": 724.67,
      "end": 729.53,
      "text": "and I've heard that there are sounds of bones crunching in the night"
    },
    {
      "start": 729.53,
      "end": 731.87,
      "text": "or even worse chips"
    },
    {
      "start": 731.87,
      "end": 734.31,
      "text": "not to mention flying toasters"
    },
    {
      "start": 734.31,
      "end": 735.77,
      "text": "that house is haunted"
    },
    {
      "start": 735.77,
      "end": 738.33,
      "text": "and that means that you're gonna need a brave"
    },
    {
      "start": 738.33,
      "end": 738.99,
      "text": "no"
    },
    {
      "start": 738.99,
      "end": 741.21,
      "text": "incredibly brave friend"
    },
    {
      "start": 741.21,
      "end": 748.95,
      "text": "스스로가 incredibly brave한 사람이라고 묘사를 한 Mark"
    },
    {
      "start": 748.95,
      "end": 752.29,
      "text": "앞으로 어떤 일이 펼쳐질지 기대가 됩니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 752.29,
      "end": 754.35,
      "text": "I hope he doesn't show up to her house"
    },
    {
      "start": 754.35,
      "end": 756.01,
      "text": "when her parents are not home"
    },
    {
      "start": 756.01,
      "end": 760.09,
      "text": "자 첫눈에 좋아하게 된 그 Mark가"
    },
    {
      "start": 760.09,
      "end": 762.41,
      "text": "과연 어떻게 반응을 할지 기대해 주시고요"
    },
    {
      "start": 762.41,
      "end": 764.89,
      "text": "오늘 여기에서 마무리해 보도록 하겠습니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 764.89,
      "end": 766.03,
      "text": "See you tomorrow"
